meanings.definition: Harvey S. Ladew (1887-1976), an American socialite, artist, and garden designer.
meanings.english_definition: Harvey S. Ladew (1887-1976), an American socialite, artist, and garden designer.

meanings.definition: Ladew Topiary Gardens, a topiary garden in Monkton, Maryland, USA, created by Harvey S. Ladew.
meanings.english_definition: Ladew Topiary Gardens, a topiary garden in Monkton, Maryland, USA, created by Harvey S. Ladew.

etymology.value: Likely derived from a German occupational surname.
